<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Zrušení rezervace</title>
</head>
<body style="background: #EEEEEE;;
padding: 20px;
margin: 0;
font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">
<div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; padding: 20px 0;">
    <div  style="max-width: 500px; padding: 30px; border-radius: 10px; background: white; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1), 0 2px 4px -2px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1);">
        <h1 style="font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bolder;
            color: #d0482b;
            margin: 0 0 20px;">Vaše rezervace byla zrušena!</h1>
        <p style="font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 30px;">Dobrý den,<br>
            je nám líto, ale musíme Vás informovat, že Vaše rezervace číslo <b>{$reservation->id}</b> u {$user->company} byla bohužel zrušena.
        </p>
        <h2 style="font-size: 16px; margin: 0px;">Detaily zrušené rezervace:</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 30px; margin-top: 2px;">
             {$reservation->ref("services", "service_id")->name} <br>
            {$reservation->start|date:"d.m.Y"}<br>
             {$reservation->start|date:"H:i"}<br>
        </p>
        <h2 style="font-size: 16px; margin: 0px;">Důvod Zrušení:</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 16px;
            margin-top: 2px;
            line-height: 30px;">
            {$reason}
        </p>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 80px; justify-content:space-between;">
            <p style="font-size: 16px;
                line-height: 30px;">S pozdravem, <br>
                <span n:if="$user->company">{$user->company}</span><br>
                <span n:if="$user->ico">IČO: {$user->ico}</span> <br>
                <span n:if="$user->dic">DIC: {$user->dic}</span> <br>
                <span n:if="$user->email">{$user->email}</span><br>
                <span n:if="$user->phone">{$user->phone}</span>
            </p>
            <!-- <img src="{$url}/assets/images/{$user->logo_url}" alt="Logo"> -->
            <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; margin-right: 20px">
                <img style="height: 100px" src="http://localhost:8000/assets/images/pomajbik-logo.png" alt="Logo">
                <!-- <img  style="height: 100px" src="{$url}/assets/images/{$user->logo_url}" alt="Logo"> -->
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>